Open main page
Click on "Sign up" button
Select role using "Select your role" bar
Enter data into the "Full name" field
Enter data into the "Email" field
Enter data into the "Password" field
Tick checkbox "I agree to the Terms & Privacy Policy"
Click on the "Sign up" button
Click on the profile icon
Click "My profile" link
Change role in the role field
Change Full name
Type in field "Link to the your profile"
Click button "Update profile"
Type data into "Old password" field
Type data into "Old password" field
Click "Change password" button
Click avatar icon
Click "Sign out" link
Enter data into email field
Enter data into password field
Click on "Sign in" button
Check that "Add course" button in header is displayed
Click on "Add course" button
Check that add course form is displayed